Third Department,

December. 1956

(December 20, 1956) In the Matter of the Claim of Arthur Albertson, Appellant against Gibson & Cushman, Inc., et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default, without costs. Foster, P. J., Bergan, Halpern and Gibson, JJ., concur.
